    "text": "SUPER SAVE PAWN\nWe Buy, Sell and Trade Anything of Value\nHOME\nSPECIALS\nABOUT\nWHAT'S NEW\nMore\nLog In\nWHAT'S NEW\nClick Here to see WHAT WE'RE BLOGGING ABOUT\nWelcome to Super Save Pawn\nWith over 75 years of combined experience, Super Save Pawn is committed to being the #1 Pawn Shop serving and supporting the local community. We pride ourselves in helpful, friendly customer service and a bright clean showroom with a variety of quality items to fit your needs. We work with our customers to provide more money to loan and buy than anyone else. We buy unwanted gold jewelry and silver, coins and more. We sell new and used jewelry, firearms, electronics, musical instruments, antiques, collectibles and more. Whether buying, selling, or trading, you are sure to get a good deal. We are looking forward to doing business with you.\n About Us\nGiving Back\nPawn Shop Specials\nAwards & \nPrograms\nServices\nContact Us\nSUPER SAVE PAWN\n2627 North Church Street Burlington NC 27217       |        336.270.8501\nEmail: supersavepawn@gmail.com\nHOURS: M-F 9AM-6PM    |    SAT. 9AM-4PM    |    SUN. CLOSED\nWebmaster Login",
